.TH YTDV "1" "December 2025" "ytdv 202209201923-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
ytdv \- Video downloader
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ytdv
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] [\fI\,URL\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ytdv
is a script for downloading videos from various online sources. It uses yt-dlp/youtube-dl to download videos in their original format or a specified quality.
.PP
The script simplifies video downloading with sensible defaults.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-help
Display help message with usage information and available options
.TP
.BR \-\-config
Generate or regenerate user configuration file with default settings
.TP
.BR \-\-version
Show script version information and exit
.TP
.BR \-\-options
Display all available command-line options
.TP
.BR \-\-debug
Enable debug mode with verbose output and command tracing (set -x)
.TP
.BR \-\-raw
Disable colorized output for plain text display
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B ytdv https://youtube.com/watch?v=VIDEO_ID
Download video from YouTube
.TP
.B ytdv "https://example.com/video"
Download video from URL
.SH FILES
.TP
.B ~/.config/myscripts/ytdv/settings.conf
User configuration file for ytdv preferences
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success
.TP
.B 1
General error
.TP
.B 4
Network connection failed
